      "webPublicationDate":"2013-10-17T07:01:49Z",
      "webTitle":"Coal executive turned climate change activist fights for seat on BHP board",
      "webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/business/2013/oct/17/coal-executive-turned-climate-change-activist-fights-for-seat-on-bhp-board",
